		"content": {
			"start": 7,
			"end": 522,
			"styles": "\n\t/* Basic scoping */\n\t@scope (.class1) {\n\t\timg {\n\t\t\tborder: 1px solid;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* Scope with limit */\n\t@scope (.class1) to (.class2) {\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* Multiple selectors */\n\t@scope (.class1, .class3) {\n\t\t.class4 {\n\t\t\tfont-weight: bold;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* Complex limit */\n\t@scope (.class5) to (.class6, .class7) {\n\t\ta {\n\t\t\ttext-decoration: underline;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* Nested scopes */\n\t@scope (.class8) {\n\t\t.class9 {\n\t\t\tpadding: 1rem;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t@scope (.class10) {\n\t\t\tspan {\n\t\t\t\tfont-weight: bold;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n",
